{
  "stem": "150.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think that evil people never think they're evil.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't think Hitler ever got up in the morning and said, today I'm really going to do something nasty.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm sure he was totally convinced that he was doing wonderful stuff cleaning up the world.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So just because the intentions are good, I think-- I think that doesn't mean anything, whatever you intend to do.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think what is important is what you actually do, and what the results are of what you do.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I think that it is important for anybody who sees this film, if they ever-- if anybody ever does, to realize that everything we do influences the future, that the future is completely liquid.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That if, for example, Hitler had not invaded Russia, today we'd probably be living in a world that would be fascist.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there would be no Jews or no blacks and no Indians left alive anywhere in the world.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And well-meaning people would probably go to a zoo on a Sunday and look in a glass cage to see a real Jew or a real black because all the rest of them would be dead.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And anything you do today will influence the future.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all I can say is we should continue trying to do whatever it is that will influence the future for the better, for the better for all, not just the better for the individual.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It is important insofar as that much of my life has revolved around causes and around things connected with Judaism.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If I were asked to define why it is that I feel myself to be a Jew, I would find it extremely difficult.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
